com.mr.http

类 MR_RequestQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mr.http.MR_RequestQueue

  • public class MR_RequestQueue
extends java.lang.Object
    A request dispatch queue with a thread pool of dispatchers. Calling add(MR_Request) will enqueue the given Request for dispatch, resolving from either cache or network on a worker thread, and then delivering a parsed response on the main thread.

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      static interface  MR_RequestQueue.RequestFilter
      A simple predicate or filter interface for Requests, for use by cancelAll(RequestFilter).

      • MR_RequestQueue

        public MR_RequestQueue(MR_Cache cache,
               MR_Network network,
               int threadPoolSize,
               MR_ResponseDelivery delivery)
        Creates the worker pool. Processing will not begin until start() is called.
        参数:
        cache - A Cache to use for persisting responses to disk
        network - A Network interface for performing HTTP requests
        threadPoolSize - Number of network dispatcher threads to create
        delivery - A ResponseDelivery interface for posting responses and errors
